column58: Charlie and alma were in the same economics class and were both entrepeneurs with business projects. charlie was part of an investment group and alma had a business plan underway that needed funding. orginally, charlie was offering half of the required money, 15k, now and the other half later if the business is going well. however, alma argued that they needed all the funds now so that they can get their business fully operational now and not have to increase their timeline. charlie was given authorisation to give all the money so he did, relunctantly. they shook hands and were the last people to leave the lecture hall. the professor said there was going to be a midterm coming up.
column141: Sven is planning on proposing to isabel and has his ring in his pocket. they are at an airport and preparing to go through security. isabel has sven hold some items as she goes through her bag and searches for her laptop. when they go through security, sven is asked by a security guard to remove everything from his pockets. he realizes that he left the ring in his pocket and decides to take advantage of the situation and proposes to isabel in the security line. she is shocked and does not seem to want to answer while being rushed by everyone trying to get through security. she grabs her items and rushes to the concourse and sven follows closely behind. when he asks her again, she says yes. they find out many people were recording the proposal and some even posted it on social media. isabel did not seem too fond of the added attention.

column58: The couple were going on holiday somewhere and liam was planning to propose. he inspected the diamond ring, which he got a couple weeks ago, at the airport and put it in his pocket. emmanuella had some overweight baggage so had to take some stuff out of her bag which liam was holding and put them in liam's suitcase. when going through the security machine, liam beeped. he was taken to a side and the security guard asked him to empty his pockets. at which point liam realised his fatal mistake. he shad the ring on him. so he took it out and said that eventhough this wasn't the time or place to be doing this, will you marry me. it took some time for emmanuella to respond but she was hyperventilating with joy and said yes. they cracked open some champagne in their first class seats and some other passengers congratulated them.
